title: The Incal
description:
The Incal is a science fiction comic book saga written by Alejandro Jodorowsky and illustrated by Moebius.

In a dystopian far future, P.I. John Difool receives the Light Incal, a crystal of enormous powers, from a dying alien.  The Incal is sought by many factions: the corrupt and decadent government, the rebel group Amok and the Church of Industrial Saints.  The series mixes space opera, metaphysics, and satire.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
